Game Instructions in English
Card Game - Worldcoin Miniapp
Objective: Guess whether the next card will be high or low.

How to play:

Connect using your World ID by clicking "Connect with World ID".
Once connected, choose your bet:
Bet High: You win if the card is 8, 9, 10, J (11), Q (12), or K (13).
Bet Low: You win if the card is Ace (1), 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, or 7.
Click the corresponding button ("Bet High" or "Bet Low").
A random card will be drawn from a standard deck (1-13 with suits: ♠, ♥, ♣, ♦).
The result will display the card and whether you won or lost.
Notes:

This is a demo game with no real betting involved.
Have fun and test your luck as many times as you like!